{"tid":2497321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國安法之後，你嘅生活有咩改變?","createTime":"2021-04-20T12:22:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T12:35:46.000Z","uid":56984,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9a67c00bfaf4e1708a2619cfe4a32fd7402cfd40","tid":2497321,"uid":56984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T12:22:52.000Z","msg":"1。見到連登仔唔再敢講光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2。見到好多政界人士退出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3。見到好多手足繼續被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4。繼續唔相信香港警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5。唔敢回望2019年，記起都好想喊，覺得自己有罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6。好多同路人移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n7。好多手足繼續默默做，默默做任，跟車，支持手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n8。連登嘅熱門都多咗好多娛樂post，行動post少咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n9。見到緬甸，明白民族性係好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10。吃喝玩樂嘅人，同唔開心嘅人都多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38672cd956c466a8c5549cc9c0b8416ca86ebd7c","tid":2497321,"uid":56984,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T12:24:32.000Z","msg":"過咗國安法之後<br />\n心情冇好過<br />\n反而2019嘅我哋更覺得開心<br />\n雖然好慘<br />\n但感受到自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01bcfb500a280db6e53071801d1cd61ab7301fce","tid":2497321,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T12:25:34.000Z","msg":"知道香港唔由我哋光復嘅話，絕無機會重光同返到二千年代咁"},{"pid":"886ac8d989e9249483fcc1b94d5e207e8db59f71","tid":2497321,"uid":56984,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T12:27:32.000Z","msg":"過咗國安法之後<br />\n食黃店嘅人都冇少到<br />\n大家仲係搵緊好多唔同方法抗爭緊<br />\n支持手足<br />\n寫信<br />\n送車<br />\n教育下